name: Cube Snake IO
description:
Play with players and try to become the biggest cube craft snake of them all!

Control your tiny cube snake and eat other players to grow larger!
Players bigger than you will be trying to eat you.
Survive and eat all them to become the biggest cube snake in the game!

Simple one touch control, CUBE SNAKE.IO made addictive gameplay!
Use splitting tactics to catch other players - or avoid them!
Use a variety of super skins!
